description:
Next, we discuss whether the Reformation had come to an end after the events told throughout this series. We recap the milestones throughout this journey and understand how many special individuals contributed along the way. The Reformation was not a singular event or fixed date, but rather a progression of ideas and beliefs that once circulated became unstoppable.

To find out more about Lineage Season II please visit our website.
